Version 1.0 of the Leap and AmberMD input generator.

To start the program simply launch main.py (requires python 3.6 or newer)

After setting all the parameters in teh three windows and pushing the Done button two files shold have been created: 
the leap input file (.leap to be processed with t or xLEaP) and the input file (md.in) to be used with sander or pmemd.

Minimization inputs not implemented yet!


List of features is still scarce. New options will be implemented in the future.
